Install the latest version of gtkmm : 
$ sudo apt-get install libgtkmm-3.0-dev

Code::Blocks
1. Open Code::Blocks -> New Project -> Empty File
2. Name your Project and make sure that the  GNU GCC compiler has been selected.
3. Add the file to an active project -> Yes.
4. Name the file as main.cpp

Reference : http://blog.mpshouse.com/?p=874
